fm: string reverseWords(string s) {         int n = s.size();         for (int i = 0; i < n; ++i) {             int j = i + 1;;             while (j < n && s[j] != ' ')                 ++j;             for (int k = i; k < (j + i) / 2; ++k)                 swap(s[k], s[j + i - k - 1]);             i = j;         }         return s;     }

vector<Interval> merge(vector<Interval> &intervals) {         vector<Interval> ret;         sort(intervals.begin(), intervals.end());         for (int i = 0; i < intervals.size(); ++i) {             if (ret.empty() || ret.back().end < intervals[i].start)                 ret.push_back(intervals[i]);             else                 ret.back().end = max(ret.back().end, intervals[i].end);         }         return ret;     }
